data.name: Vortexium Network
data.description:
Welcome to Vortexium Network! 

A new Minecraft and Eaglercraft era is rising, Vortexium Network brand new server working to take CrackedPVPs place, We are here trying to create a super Enjoyable, Kind and Fair Community.

Just so you know this server is going to be a tiny bit "pay to win" because we need the money to be able to our own vps and hopfully make the server even better.

Server Features
🍩 DonutSMP-A DonutSMP copy made from scratch expect from luckperms and maps.
VortexiumSMP*-A SMP made just for Vortexium Networks theme with custom made plugins, custom made generations!
BoxPVP-Mine, Grind, Upgrade!

Boxpvp released
Why players Should join Vortexium:

A friendly, active community

Custom features and Weekly fun events**

Hop on and join the fun!
